commit.message:
Fix PR ada/97504 on hppa*-*-hpux*.

2020-11-29  John David Anglin  <danglin@gcc.gnu.org>

gcc/ada/
	PR ada/97504
	* Makefile.rtl (LIBGNAT_TARGET_PAIRS) <hppa*-*-hpux*>: Use wraplf
	version of Aux_Long_Long_Float.
